{
  "id": "69b0eeebf6d4f8f6d0f5ff20",
  "title": "日本語のアラビア文字翻字",
  "created": 1773203181,
  "updated": 1773214969,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b0eeebf6d4f8f6d0f5ff20",
      "text": "日本語のアラビア文字翻字",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203181,
      "updated": 1773203181
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0eeee000000000086e626",
      "text": "#怪文書の書き方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203181,
      "updated": 1773203186
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0eef3000000000086e628",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203186,
      "updated": 1773203186
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0ef03000000000086e62a",
      "text": "変な字形にならないように既存のやり方とは違うやり方を用いる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203202,
      "updated": 1773203226
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0ef1d000000000086e62c",
      "text": "\t例えば、　را\t　（ra）よりも　لا　（la）の方が字形が良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203229,
      "updated": 1773203407
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0ef03000000000086e62b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203202,
      "updated": 1773203202
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0eef3000000000086e629",
      "text": "table:あいえうお",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203186,
      "updated": 1773203442
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0eff2000000000086e62d",
      "text": "\t\tあ\tい・え\tう・お\t\tあ\tい・え\tう・お",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203442,
      "updated": 1773204455
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f544000000000086e640",
      "text": "\tあ\tعا\tعي\tعو\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773204804,
      "updated": 1773205796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f0ae000000000086e62e",
      "text": "\tか\tكا\tكي\tكي\tが\tقا\tقي\tقو",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203629,
      "updated": 1773205738
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0eeef000000000086e627",
      "text": "\tさ\tسا\tسي\tسو\tざ\tظا\tظي\tظو",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203182,
      "updated": 1773205643
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f146000000000086e631",
      "text": "\tた\tتا\tتي\tتو\tだ\tضا\tضي\tضو",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203781,
      "updated": 1773205669
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f11d000000000086e630",
      "text": "\tな\tنا\tني\tنو\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203740,
      "updated": 1773203841
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f1d7000000000086e633",
      "text": "\tは\tها\tهي\tهو\tば\tبا\tبي\tبو",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203927,
      "updated": 1773205203
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f16e000000000086e632",
      "text": "\tま\tما\tمي\tمو\tば\tپا\tپي\tپو",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203822,
      "updated": 1773205226
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f1f7000000000086e635",
      "text": "\tや\tيا\t\tيو\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773203958,
      "updated": 1773204273
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f23c000000000086e637",
      "text": "\tら\tلا\tلي\tليو\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773204028,
      "updated": 1773204309
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f309000000000086e63d",
      "text": "\tわ\tفا\tفي\tفو\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773204233,
      "updated": 1773204404
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f2a3000000000086e63c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773204130,
      "updated": 1773204130
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f937000000000086e642",
      "text": "音韻体系が違いすぎるので、適合する文字があまり無い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773205815,
      "updated": 1773205858
    },
    {
      "id": "69b106d3000000000086e68c",
      "text": "\t無理矢理当てはめてみたが、当てはまるものを選ぶこと自体が難しい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773209299,
      "updated": 1773209337
    },
    {
      "id": "69b106e9000000000086e68d",
      "text": "\t語尾にしかつかないものまである。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773209321,
      "updated": 1773209333
    },
    {
      "id": "69b106fe000000000086e68e",
      "text": "\t\t子音は語頭につけたいのに。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773209341,
      "updated": 1773209350
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0f950000000000086e644",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773205839,
      "updated": 1773206380
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fb6d000000000086e645",
      "text": "標準アラビア語の子音音素",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773206380,
      "updated": 1773206395
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fb71000000000086e650",
      "text": "table:アラビア語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773206385,
      "updated": 1773206390
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e675",
      "text": "  \t\t\t強調なし\t強調音\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208185
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e676",
      "text": " \t\t唇音\t歯/歯茎\t歯/歯茎\t硬口蓋音\t軟口蓋/口蓋垂\t咽頭音\t声門音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208182
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e677",
      "text": " 鼻音\t\tم m\tن n\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208026
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e678",
      "text": " 閉鎖音\t無声\t\tت t\tط tˤ\t\tك k / ق q\t\tء ʔ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208108
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e679",
      "text": " \t有声\tب b\tد d\tض dˤ\tج dʒ\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208657
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e67a",
      "text": " 摩擦音\t無声\tف f\tث θ / س s\t- / ص sˤ\tش ʃ\tخ x ~ χ\tح ħ\tه h",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208107
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e67b",
      "text": " \t有声\t\tذ ð / ز z\tظ ðˤ / -\t\tغ ɣ ~  ʁ\tع ʕ\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208653
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e67c",
      "text": " 震え音\t\t\t- / ر r\tر rˤ / -\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208120
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e67d",
      "text": " 接近音\t\t\tل l\tل lˤ\tي j\tو w / -\t\t ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773208070
    },
    {
      "id": "69b0fff6000000000086e67e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773207541,
      "updated": 1773207541
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10311000000000086e67f",
      "text": "↑ 音の対立の仕方や分け方が異なりすぎて音声学的概念を当てはめようとすると表が汚くなる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773208336,
      "updated": 1773208392
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10311000000000086e680",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773208337,
      "updated": 1773208337
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10351000000000086e681",
      "text": "table:アラビア語 (右にあるものは3個つなげたもの)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773208401,
      "updated": 1773209911
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10f5a000000000086e788",
      "text": "\tء\tʔ\tءءء",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773211481,
      "updated": 1773211481
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10c15000000000086e6bb",
      "text": "\tا\tal\tااا\t尾字のみ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773210645,
      "updated": 1773211526
    },
    {
      "id": "69b11489000000000086e7cc",
      "text": "\tل\tl\tللل\tن\tn\tننن\tي\tj\tييي\tك\tk\tككك",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773212809,
      "updated": 1773214786
    },
    {
      "id": "69b11c70000000000086e838",
      "text": "\tر\tr\tررر\tز\tz\tززز\tو\tw\tووو\tق\tq\tققق",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773214832,
      "updated": 1773214833
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1188e000000000086e805",
      "text": "\tس\ts\tسسس\tش\tʃ\tششش",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773213837,
      "updated": 1773213837
    },
    {
      "id": "69b118a1000000000086e80a",
      "text": "\tص\tsˤ\tصصص\tض\tdˤ\tضضض\tظ\tðˤ\tظظظ\tط\ttˤ\tططط",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773213857,
      "updated": 1773214969
    },
    {
      "id": "69b118a4000000000086e80c",
      "text": "\tد\td\tددد\tذ\tð\tذذذ\tت\tt\tتتت\tث\tθ\tثثث",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773213860,
      "updated": 1773213860
    },
    {
      "id": "69b11a7f000000000086e825",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\tف\tf\tففف\tب\tb\tببب",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773214335,
      "updated": 1773214884
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1100b000000000086e78a",
      "text": "\tح\tħ\tححح\tخ\tx\tخخخ\tج\tdʒ\tججج",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773211658,
      "updated": 1773213115
    },
    {
      "id": "69b11690000000000086e7dc",
      "text": "\tع\tʕ\tععع\tغ\tɣ\tغغغ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773213327,
      "updated": 1773213327
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10dd4000000000086e755",
      "text": "\tم\tm\tممم",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773211092,
      "updated": 1773211092
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10ded000000000086e768",
      "text": "\tه\th\tههه",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773211116,
      "updated": 1773211116
    },
    {
      "id": "69b10793000000000086e695",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773209491,
